Package frclib.dataprocessor

Class FrcColor

java.lang.Object
trclib.dataprocessor.TrcColor
frclib.dataprocessor.FrcColor
public class FrcColor extends TrcColor
This class implements an FRC specific color object. It extends TrcColor so it can be used by the rest of trclib. It also includes an embedded WPILib Color object so it can be used by WPILib as well.
